<i>No.</i>

781
01:12:21,919 --> 01:12:23,079
<i>You're not dead.</i>

782
01:12:24,319 --> 01:12:26,399
<i>You're not even sick.</i>

783
01:12:26,519 --> 01:12:27,959
But I am, my darling.

784
01:12:29,919 --> 01:12:30,959
I am sick.

785
01:12:32,559 --> 01:12:33,879
Sick like you was.

786
01:12:33,999 --> 01:12:36,079
<i>No. Not true.</i>

787
01:12:36,199 --> 01:12:38,519
<i>I know it.
You've got to live, Daddy.</i>

788
01:12:41,719 --> 01:12:43,759
<i>You let the fire go out.</i>

789
01:12:45,879 --> 01:12:48,399
Light the fire again
and get warm,

790
01:12:48,519 --> 01:12:51,639
and you will see
that you must live.

791
