Oh, and the doctor
at St Thomas's

806
01:15:34,839 --> 01:15:36,799
who you sent me to
for the second opinion,

807
01:15:36,919 --> 01:15:38,359
second set of X-rays?

808
01:15:39,439 --> 01:15:41,439
A maid of honour
at the same wedding.

809
01:15:42,599 --> 01:15:44,479
All so very well
fucking connected.

810
01:15:46,679 --> 01:15:48,359
On your knees, Holford.

811
01:15:54,559 --> 01:15:56,919
I'm guessing you people
all decided

812
01:15:57,039 --> 01:15:59,279
that the only person

813
01:15:59,399 --> 01:16:01,159
who could ever kill
Tommy Shelby. <i>..</i>

814
01:16:02,719 --> 01:16:04,279
<i>..</i> .Is Tommy Shelby himself.

815
01:16:07,719 --> 01:16:10,039
You made me believe
death was coming.

816
01:16:10,159 --> 01:16:12,639
Let my nature do the rest,
eh?

817
01:16:17,679 --> 01:16:20,199
You may not have tuberculoma,
Mr Shelby...

818
01:16:21,279 --> 01:16:22,639
<i>...but</i> you are sick.

819
01:16:24,159 --> 01:16:25,279
I know you.

820
01:16:26,839 --> 01:16:28,839
You are sick with guilt.

821
01:16:30,639 --> 01:16:33,599
Sick of death at your own hand.

822
01:16:35,119 --> 01:16:36,559
Sick of who you were.

823
01:16:39,719 --> 01:16:41,399
You are no longer
the kind of man

824
01:16:41,519 --> 01:16:43,879
who would kill another man
in cold blood.

825
01:16:49,679 --> 01:16:53,839
Tommy, you have been
on a journey,

826
01:16:53,959 --> 01:16:56,919
from the backstreets
to the corridors of power.

827
01:17:00,039 --> 01:17:01,199
You cannot go back.

828
01:17:03,039 --> 01:17:04,359
You are a different man.

829
01:17:06,479 --> 01:17:08,639
The gun no longer belongs
in your hand.

830
01:17:15,399 --> 01:17:16,959
Oh, but I am back.

831
01:17:20,079 --> 01:17:22,559
Back from under the ground.

